(FMR).

For XM1225 Aviation Proximity Explosive (APEX), proposals were requested from Industry to develop proximity airburst tactical cartridges that will meet Army
Performance Specifications for antipersonnel and Counter UAS. The Government will award Other Transaction Agreement (OTA) contracts to support development and
testing for the fielding of the proximity airburst ammunition, with an option to award low-rate manufacturing.

