methodologies to provide SLV and Human-Machine Integration (HMI) assessments of Army ground, aviation, munitions, and
Soldier priority systems and technologies for AFC and Program Executive Offices (PEOs). For DEVCOM Centers/ARL, will
continue to provide kinetic and non-kinetic analyses. Will also provide cyber and electromagnetic warfare threat emulation and
integrated system-level vulnerability and survivability assessments to enable technology development, inform prototype and
system design decisions and reduce technology risks through experimentation and Testing and Evaluation (T&E) of ground,
aviation, munitions and Soldier technologies.
