on preventing exploitation/reverse engineering (RE) of U.S. systems lost or captured on the battlefield or sold via Foreign Military Sales (FMS) or Direct Commercial
Sales (DCS). In support of this mission, PT's classified efforts are focused on independent AT Validation and Verification (V&V) activities with Army programs, AT/RE
